channel.title: Orphaned case error:
channel.description:
[b] Hai guys, I'm coding a 508 server, and I'm about 70% done with full GodWars. But I keep getting this error when I try to add the entrance to the dungeon. I've tried moving it, moving brackets above and below; nothing works :mad:
If you could please help, I'd be very gratefull.[/b]
[b]Error:[/b] [code].\palidino76\rs2\io\packets\ObjectOption2.java:44: orphaned case case 26342: ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . . [/code]

item.title: Orphaned case error:
item.dc:creator: @slomifier slomifier
item.description:
@slomifier wrote:

Ya, if you get an orphaned case error, it means that you have a case outside of a switch, which is obviously illegal

Read full topic

item.title: Orphaned case error:
item.dc:creator: @Razr1 Razr`
item.description:
@Razr1 wrote:

All cases need to be placed inside a switch statement.

Read full topic
